hopobject.body: We'd like to offer you the job atorvastatin calcium tablets side effects I worked for a large HMO during those years, and would note that as a quality-improvement measure we HMO physicians got better and better at double-checking on ourselves, to prove that we were documenting blood pressure elevations, and then promptly treating the patients for hypertension, and not procrastinating. After a decade or so, our outcome data also began to show a nice signal about better medication compliance, and fewer strokes and MI deaths among our patients, to reassure ourselves that we were making progress.
